gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Magic 115, Jazz 107
gameRecap.excerpt: The Magic defeated the Jazz, 115-107. Paolo Banchero led the way with 29 points, nine rebounds, and six assists for the Magic, with Jalen Suggs adding 15 points (4-7 3PM) and two rebounds in the victory. John Collins tallied 19 points and 10 rebounds for the Jazz in the losing effort. The Magic improve to 34-26, while the Jazz fall to 27-33.
